name: Furry Fields Forever #6
description:
This is #6 of Furry Fields Forever

Listening to the Beatles and was working on creating generative fields. Working with a few newer color palettes and this came to view. 

The piece is 1000 x 1000 in order to ensure the ability to display on larger displays.
